Text:
Yikes - WARNING !  
Wear eye protection or risk being blinded.  It's BAD.
I uploaded this set just for you ElmoGunch - I knew you would appreciate it!

I was going to comment on everything that had already been commented on, degrading you, simply because I can't sleep. But this shit is ridiculous. You have over 9000 photo sets that I'm even ashamed to look at the descriptions of, let alone plaster my good name upon their pages.

Seriously, shadowyad, I wish you had a girlfriend for the sake of all men everywhere. Having this amount of dedication to photos of celebrities that Women's Health would run as covers isn't right.
